Haló?

114
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:17,740
Haló?

115
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:22,850
Si to ty, Juna?

116
00:10:23,650 --> 00:10:26,050
Nevidíš moje číslo na displeji?

117
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:29,060
Mám to zablokované.

118
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:29,920
Hups

